{"tid":875866,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【極掃興】約小女友食浪漫晚餐 10歲小情聖慘被餐廳趕出店外","createTime":"2018-10-25T07:55:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T09:42:48.000Z","uid":130626,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6dcd1e9999fd8dc88f83b205b006bdf604785ae5","tid":875866,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T07:55:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181025/large/1540407782_1aa8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181025%2Flarge%2F1540407782_1aa8.jpg&h=d3c0f7a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181025/large/1540407782_8adb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181025%2Flarge%2F1540407782_8adb.jpg&h=26fc6363&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蘇格蘭一名10歲男孩，情竇初開，約小女友到愛丁堡的Nando&rsquo;s餐廳享受浪漫晚餐，怎料餐廳指13歲以下小童在沒有成人陪同下，不能在餐廳內用餐，把他們趕出店外，可憐一對小情人只可坐在長凳上吃薯條雞翼。<br />\n<br />\n事件由男孩的姐姐揭發。她在Twitter上發文說，她的小弟弟只有10歲，約了他的小女友去Nando&rsquo;s，但店方以他們不足13歲為由，不許他們坐在店內，要他們外賣食物，只可坐在店外長凳進食。她表示那一餐是由其弟弟請客，她最後說：「Nando&rsquo;s可恥！」<br />\n<br />\nNando&rsquo;s事後就「限制了該位小男士的風格」而致歉，但證實這是法例所限。店方發言人說：「我們都知道無人會想拖著父母出來拍拖，但不幸地，我店有酒牌，而蘇格蘭法例規定發牌條件是13歲以下孩童必須由成人陪同。」<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》 <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181025/58832921\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181025%2F58832921&d=m%2F180F9IkiAbVluShB6eh4M9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=8d78b026\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181025%2F58832921&h=11285c27\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181025/58832921</a>"},{"pid":"e4750bbee8e09571aa460a5a82cb956f3474e32a","tid":875866,"uid":136186,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T07:59:06.000Z","msg":"人哋10歲就食女扑嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f91c4d82c25718d7e2fbe0447104ffefc8ebec0","tid":875866,"uid":134474,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T08:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叫連登仔情何以堪"},{"pid":"6ae212848198fe3804529464b8dd5965be206a2e","tid":875866,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T08:17:56.000Z","msg":"10 歲就屌打感情台以外連登仔"},{"pid":"4d222744dfe86f8a14268bc1fb5166bf9dc51d74","tid":875866,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T08:25:42.000Z","msg":"咁都屌人可恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我店有酒牌，而蘇格蘭法例規定發牌條件是13歲以下孩童必須由成人陪同。<br />\n<br />\n得10歲都唔睇住佢由佢周圍走"},{"pid":"36c2b8024fae40aaeca0df0a0ddb628feaadefa5","tid":875866,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T08:41:19.000Z","msg":"好掛住Nando&rsquo;s啲雞同汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c00b99ef64e27e590bc320c48d5cb1c36bc2ff52","tid":875866,"uid":68220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6ae212848198fe3804529464b8dd5965be206a2e","tid":875866,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T08:17:56.000Z","msg":"10 歲就屌打感情台以外連登仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T08:41:33.000Z","msg":"感情台係under創意台的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成班人係度FF"},{"pid":"80bd621df6be4fcdf91997469c209c56df6f2b09","tid":875866,"uid":35066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T08:45:26.000Z","msg":"Nando&rsquo;s <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係澳洲每星期食一次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/so